      <div id="aboutAuthor" class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/author/show/776.Michael_Lewis">About Michael   Lewis</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class='bookAuthorProfile'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/776.Michael_Lewis"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1317447168p3/776.jpg);'></div>
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__widgetContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__name'>
<a href="/author/show/776.Michael_Lewis">Michael   Lewis
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__followerCount'>
11,030
followers
</div>

</div>
</div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer14582746162172464570"><strong>Michael Lewis</strong>, the best-selling author of <em>Liar’s Poker</em>, <em>The Money Culture</em>, <em>The New New Thing</em>, <em>Moneyball</em>, <em>The Blind Side</em>, <em>Panic</em>, <em>Home Game</em>, <em>The Big Short</em>, and <em>Boomerang</em>, among other works, lives in Berkeley, California, with his wife and three children.</span>

</div>
</div>

<div class="clear"></div></div></div><div class="bigBoxBottom"></div></div>

  

